text: pdfimages is an open-source command-line utility for extracting images from PDF files. It is freely available as part of poppler-utils and xpdf-utils, and included in many Linux distributions. pdfimages originates from the xpdf package. The Poppler software package, which is derived from xpdf, also includes an implementation of pdfimages. ==See also== * List of PDF software ==References== ==External links== * Poppler utils 0.37 2015 for Windows Category:Graphics-related software for Linux Category:Free PDF software
title: Pdfimages
